# keyscrub.patch — cross-platform memory-key scrub (VC_ENABLE_KEYSCRUB)
#
# Paths are relative to src/ (apply with -p1 from src/). New files (Common/KeyScrub.{c,h},
# Core/KeyScrubEvents.{h,cpp}) apply onto stock VeraCrypt 1.26.29 as-is. The hunks in
# CommandLineInterface.cpp and HardwareKeyFactor.{c,h} build on this fork's existing
# HardwareKeyFactor series (as every incremental patch here does); apply that series first, or use
# patches/ALL-changes-vs-1.26.29.patch for the cumulative onto-stock diff. Verified to apply cleanly
# onto the fork baseline. See docs/MEMORY-SCRUB.md.
#
